metadata.name: Primeiro Dia #1/21
metadata.description:
Tribute to Primeiro Dia song by Sergio Godinho, Portuguese songwriter master. 

A song about the different stages of life, the struggles and the motivation for each one of us. Each phase of life on each stanza. 

This song has been with me since I'm a child and continues to be present. It can be seen as perfect summary of a life span and I think this photo can portray that journey
